{"tid":165484,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"點解咁多連登仔憎TB","createTime":"2017-03-21T11:33:43.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-27T02:33:46.000Z","uid":88032,"like":12,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"73904aa90431aea66b5e6bde010ab765b3c4cb89","tid":165484,"uid":88032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T11:33:43.000Z","msg":"我唔憎TB<br />\n我係厭惡TB<br />\n你唔會憎舊屎，但你會厭惡舊屎<br />\n我對TB既感覺就好似對屎既感覺<br />\nTB或者基佬，佢地肯出櫃，對人類呢個物種係好事<br />\n因為呢D屎放棄左繁殖下一代呢個Option，換言之佢地搞基呢D DNA將會由佢地呢一代斷後<br />\n咁過多幾代之後，天生有屎DNA既人類就變得越黎越少<br />\n有屎DNA既人類會變得越黎越少數，去到最後比人類既DNA長河排擠<br />\n就好似當年既尼安德特人咁，完全比智人取代<br />\n同埋少左TB或者基佬繁殖，你將來你既下一代就少左對手同佢地競爭社會資源，你既下一代變相存活率就可以高D，你既DNA就可以流傳落去<br />\n咁唔係一件好事黎咩？"},{"pid":"583d3f4c622cccbaa3cc9b909c069aac6cc906fc","tid":165484,"uid":45821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T11:35:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/21/193547_7a23cf25a547ad9d2ae11bbe5c4f15c3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F21%2F193547_7a23cf25a547ad9d2ae11bbe5c4f15c3.jpg&h=407853ba&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d50c5854cfdb2ade5117128078b32a261392bbf1","tid":165484,"uid":88032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T11:40:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d146d95dbeb6034a5b9232802350cfd7a5f9f78","tid":165484,"uid":89478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T11:43:23.000Z","msg":"tb死全家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab05d64df49d34d5bae78b0403fb69ad5daabeba","tid":165484,"uid":88032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T11:52:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29a80fed6ecf501feba1972a889ef359596e005c","tid":165484,"uid":88032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T11:57:35.000Z"